title: Over/Under: Early 2017 Predictions
itunes:title: Over/Under: Early 2017 Predictions
description:
A room filled with some heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the news from around the NFL including the latest on the Raiders possible relocation to Las Vegas, and reports that the Saints may be interested in Johnny Manziel. Then the heroes look ahead to the season and make some early predictions in a friendly game of over/under. Plus, an update on the Derek Carr Twitter saga.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
